name: Pretty Flower Lavender Pouch, cream
description:
The Pretty Flower Lavender Pouch is inspired by Laura Felicity's Pretty Flower design.

Each pouch is made from excess silk screen printed fabric from the Pretty Flower lampshades and converted into small lavender bags perfect for cloth drawers.

Each pouch is filled with 100% British-Grown lavender and hand stitched creating a delicate, handmade finish.

Dimensions: 9cm diameter

Material: 100% Cotton Front, 100% Polyester Sateen Back
100% British-Grown Lavender

Please note that each pouch is different due to being made from upcycled fabrics from Laura Felicity.  
The pouch you receive may not be identical to that in the image on this website, making this unique lavender pouch truly one of a kind.

name: Pretty Flower Wallpaper 10m Roll
description:
*This product is Made To Order*

Available in three colours, the Pretty Flower wallpaper has been designed with enchanted goodness.  Featured in Laura Felicity's Modern Elegance Bespoke wallpaper, this one layered, yet intriguing silk screen print enables the purchaser to get enticed within Pretty Flower's design, and its wonderland of beautiful flowers.

The Pretty Flower pattern has been screen printed onto 160gsm wallpaper

Dimensions: 52cm x 10m roll
Repeat across: 41cm
Repeat down: 82cm

This wallpaper can be supplied in the standard 10m rolls or panels made to measure for your space.  
Please get in contact for more information.

name: Geometric Flower Wallpaper 10m Roll
description:
*This product is Made To order*

Available in three colours, Laura Felicity's Geometric Flower wallpaper is a two layered print inspired by geometric flower trestles and natural floral forms.  
This pattern has many contrasting yet complimenting aspects to the design, and creates and intriguing and comfortable atmosphere.

The Geometric Flower pattern has been screen printed onto 160gsm wallpaper

Dimensions: 52cm x 10m roll
Repeat across:35cm
Repeat down: 70cm

This wallpaper can be supplied in the standard 10m rolls or panels made to measure for your space.  Please get in contact for more information.

name: Dotty Bird Wallpaper 10m Roll
description:
*This product is Made To Order*

Available in three colours, the Dotty Bird wallpaper is a two layered screen print combining sporadically placed polka dots, underneath delicate line drawn imagery.  Featuring two chirpy birds and a beautiful birdcage immersed around branches and flowers, this wallpaper creates a cheeky, yet romantically sophisticated pattern.

The Dotty Bird pattern has been screen printed on to 160gsm wallpaper.

Dimensions: 52cm x 10m roll
Repeat across:37.5cm
Repeat down: 74cm

This wallpaper can be supplied in the standard 10m rolls or panels made to measure for your space.  Please get in contact for more information.

name: Hand Cut Alphabet Initial Print
description:
Taking inspiration from the hand cut approach in Laura Felicity's Geometric Flutter Art Print, she has hand cut fluttering birds out of her Dotty Bird wallpaper and arranging each bird into a single initial and finished by machine embroidering the bird formation onto card backing.

Something a little extra special about this Print is that it can be personalised.  Laura Felicity can design initials from A-Z for you or someone close to you, making it a perfect gift and displayed feature for the home.

This print has the option of it's own 3D frame (at an additional price).

Dimensions: 25cm x 25cm

Simply select your colour and frame perefence and Laura Felicity will contact you after your purchase, to ask what your initial you would like made.

Bespoke commissions are available for this product.

name: Hand Cut Butterfly Print
description:
Taking inspiration from the hand cut approach in Laura Felicity's Geometric Flutter Art Print, she has hand cut different sized butterflies out of her Pretty Flower wallpaper and arranging each butterfly to create a linear formation and finished by machine embroidering the butterflies onto card backing.

Something a little extra special about this print is one of the butterflies has been hand cut from the Modern Elegance Art Print where there is an overlay of gold or silver foil, depending on the colour you choose.  

This print has the option of it's own 3D frame (at an additional price-see below).

Available in three colours.

Dimensions: 25cm x 25cm

Bespoke commissions are available for this product.

name: Hand Cut Heart Print
description:
Taking inspiration from the hand cut approach in Laura Felicity's Geometric Flutter Art Print, she has hand cut heart shapes out of her Geometric Flower wallpaper and arranging each heart into a larger hollowed heart.  

This print is finished by machine embroidering the hearts onto card backing.

With the focus of this piece being a decorative feature for the home, it can also be a subtle reminder to show how much you appreciate/or are appreciated by that someone extra special. 

This print has the option of it's own 3D frame (at an additional price-see below).

Available in three colours.

Dimensions: 25cm x 25cm

Bespoke commissions are available for this product.

name: Lace Embedded Coasters
description:
These plaster coasters have been designed with a little vintage goodness.

Creating something fragile yet functional with a combination of sort textiles and hard materials, Laura Felicity has created a technique to embed beautiful silk flower lace patterns within the surface plaster.

Each coaster is handmade, meaning the dimensions may change ever so slightly.

The coasters come with three lace colour options; Dusky Pink, Black, or Cream.

Please note that the lace is from different sourced areas, and so patterns and colours may change slightly. They are backed with a cork layer, to protect your surfaces and prevent slipping.

Each coaster has been sprayed with two protective layers for everyday use. However, we advise for the coasters to be cleaned or wiped with a damp cloth if stained. Please do not risk soaking or putting the coasters in the dishwasher.

Dimensions: 9.5cm diameter x 4mm thickness.
